# Copy to .env.local and fill in. Add the same vars in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables.

# Contact form delivery (Web3Forms — free, no domain/DNS needed).
# Get a key at https://web3forms.com: enter hello.barelycode@gmail.com, the key is
# emailed instantly. The form submits from the browser, so the key is PUBLIC by design
# (Web3Forms expects this — protect it with the domain allowlist + spam settings in
# their dashboard). Hence the NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix. Until set, submissions only log.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
